        <Summary>Service menus for developing PiSi packages</Summary>
        <Description>PiSi Developer-Tools is a collection of usefull tools to make building PiSi packages easier. It provides service menus (only Dolphin) for package building, package info, pisi repository indexer and checksum calculator. PiSi Developer-Tools is also part of the German PiSi book named "HowTo - PiSi" - written form Gürkan ZENGIN, from PardusUser.de</Description>
        <Archive type="tarbz2" sha1sum="2b0a21d7f10a9a0a5f19fcc4def632ff3ac40ef9">http://pakete.pardususer.de/quellarchive/pisi-developer-tools-1.3.tar.bz2</Archive>
    </Source>

    <Package>
        <Name>pisi-developer-tools</Name>
        <RuntimeDependencies>
            <Dependency>bash</Dependency>
            <Dependency>coreutils</Dependency>
            <Dependency>firefox</Dependency>
            <Dependency>grep</Dependency>
            <Dependency>kdebase</Dependency>
            <Dependency>sed</Dependency>
        </RuntimeDependencies>
        <Files>
            <Path fileType="data">/usr/kde/4/share/apps/</Path>
            <Path fileType="data">/usr/kde/4/share/kde4/services/ServiceMenus/</Path>
